ch Triangle Park NC USA Selected papers from ISCIS VIII will be published in the journal Information Sciences Elsevier North Holland Poster Submission Submit five camera ready copies of page extended abstract with an accompanying letter by July to the address given Information For required writing format further information and announcements contact ISCIS VIII Ugur Halici of Electrical and Electronics METU Ankara Turkey Tel Ext Fax Email or